stepik-selenium-page-object-tests
This is a practice project for automated testing using Selenium and Pytest. It was created as part of a Stepik course.

What's in the project
Tests are written using the Page Object pattern

All page classes are stored in the pages folder

Selectors are stored in a separate locators.py file

How to run the tests
Install the dependencies:

nginx
Copy
Edit
pip install -r requirements.txt
Run tests marked with need_review:

arduino
Copy
Edit
pytest -v --tb=line --language=en -m need_review
Library versions
pytest==5.1.1

selenium==3.14.0

What is being tested
Adding a product to the basket

Navigating to the login page

Checking that the basket is empty

Behavior of a guest user and a logged-in user

